Filters.Description: Restrictions for what files should be pulled from the source.

Folders.Description: Identifiers for the source folders to pull all files from recursively.

FirstExecutionFrom.Description: The start date for objects to import in the first flow run. Epoch or ISO timestamp format is supported.

Object.Description: The name of the object to pull from the data source.

ScheduleExpression.Description: How often the data should be pulled from data source.

Key.Description: A key to identify the tag.

Value.Description: Corresponding tag value for the key.

DataIntegrationArn.Description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the data integration.

FileConfiguration.Description: The configuration for what files should be pulled from the source.

Id.Description: The unique identifer of the data integration.

KmsKey.Description: The KMS key of the data integration.

Name.Description: The name of the data integration.

ObjectConfiguration.Description: The configuration for what data should be pulled from the source.

ScheduleConfig.Description: The name of the data and how often it should be pulled from the source.

SourceURI.Description: The URI of the data source.

Tags.Description: The tags (keys and values) associated with the data integration.

Key.Description: A key to identify the metadata.

Value.Description: Corresponding metadata value for the key.

Key.Description: A key to identify the tag.

Value.Description: Corresponding tag value for the key.

EventBridgeBus.Description: The Amazon Eventbridge bus for the event integration.

EventFilter.Description: The EventFilter (source) associated with the event integration.

EventIntegrationArn.Description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the event integration.

Name.Description: The name of the event integration.

Tags.Description: The tags (keys and values) associated with the event integration.
